  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437060/extras/5f39b1442c9972408752de17fd14f18a.avif?t=1739237715\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437060/extras_big/5f39b1442c9972408752de17fd14f18a.avif?t=1739237715 width=800 height=114 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437060/extras/7c0c0dd8b936c93d6944c987f6f5d4ce.avif?t=1739237715\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437060/extras_big/7c0c0dd8b936c93d6944c987f6f5d4ce.avif?t=1739237715 width=800 height=192 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Black Fairy Tale is a game that enhances abilities and features automatic combat.（Gameplay imitates and learns keyboard warriors）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deceived Little Red Riding Hood, vengeful Yuriosa, righteous female Taoist</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose a girl and walk through a forest full of monsters, only through battle can you survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each time you defeat an enemy, you can choose a card that will have different ways of strengthening.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437060/extras/4e1b5de88d37a35dbcee4ce4de5643b4.poster.avif?t=1739237715\" width=800 height=622 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437060/extras/4e1b5de88d37a35dbcee4ce4de5643b4.webm?t=1739237715\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437060/extras/4e1b5de88d37a35dbcee4ce4de5643b4.mp4?t=1739237715\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437060/extras/00c669b765671b47faa2c5a0ba612985.avif?t=1739237715\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437060/extras_big/00c669b765671b47faa2c5a0ba612985.avif?t=1739237715 width=800 height=119 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast paced and easy placement battles, equipped with a variety of weapons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A shield that combines offense and defense, a potion that restores life, and a gemstone that constantly appreciates in value</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437060/extras/fbdc221cab735fad26e2450f0b935063.poster.avif?t=1739237715\" width=800 height=622 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437060/extras/fbdc221cab735fad26e2450f0b935063.webm?t=1739237715\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437060/extras/fbdc221cab735fad26e2450f0b935063.mp4?t=1739237715\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are a wide variety of genres to choose from, with different experiences in each battle, and various artifacts to assist.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437060/extras/d42fe39a7453f7455d94305711180b49.poster.avif?t=1739237715\" width=620 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437060/extras/d42fe39a7453f7455d94305711180b49.webm?t=1739237715\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437060/extras/d42fe39a7453f7455d94305711180b49.mp4?t=1739237715\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every girl has her own unique trick, which may change the core of your construction.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437060/extras/b70db729daf1ce9262dd35cdadd59c1e.poster.avif?t=1739237715\" width=540 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437060/extras/b70db729daf1ce9262dd35cdadd59c1e.webm?t=1739237715\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437060/extras/b70db729daf1ce9262dd35cdadd59c1e.mp4?t=1739237715\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The crisis ridden forest is also full of opportunities, who wouldn't want to be intimate with the succubus boss?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437060/extras/8d3b6d57f73a66ba5638c3738e3a1096.avif?t=1739237715\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437060/extras_big/8d3b6d57f73a66ba5638c3738e3a1096.avif?t=1739237715 width=800 height=454 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437060/extras/11025612f6a0dd08e0d2666d20f9a1e9.avif?t=1739237715\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437060/extras_big/11025612f6a0dd08e0d2666d20f9a1e9.avif?t=1739237715 width=800 height=119 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every girl in a fairy tale has a tragic past, and their future will be rewritten by you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(Mainly because the development was rushed and there was no time to do the plot)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437060/extras/ef6644a404a396c5883e7edced117325.poster.avif?t=1739237715\" width=540 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437060/extras/ef6644a404a396c5883e7edced117325.webm?t=1739237715\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437060/extras/ef6644a404a396c5883e7edced117325.mp4?t=1739237715\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
